      &lt;p&gt;If you are familiar to &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.scala-sbt.org/0.13/docs/Command-Line-Reference.html#Configuration-level+tasks&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;
    
    </summary>
    
    
